OL,3,CTravellers face Easter bank holiday
OL,4,Cchaos after major train disruption
OL,6,FRail passengers faced bank holiday
OL,7,Fchaos on trains across South Wales due
OL,8,Fto power issues on the mainline.
OL,10,FAll services between and were
OL,11,Fsuspended this morning (Monday) due to
OL,12,Fa signalling fault from an electrical
OL,13,Fissue - believed to have been caused
OL,14,Fby a cable theft.
OL,16,FNational Rail says the issue has now
OL,17,Fbeen resolved and services have
OL,18,Frecommenced as usual.
OL,20,FA 'Do Not Travel' notice was issued
OL,21,Fbut has since been lifted.
