OL,3,CTravellers face Easter bank holiday
OL,4,Cchaos after major train disruption
OL,6,F"We will look to reintroduce services
OL,7,Ffrom 12.30 onwards and advise
OL,8,Fpassengers to check journey planners
OL,9,Fbefore they travel."
OL,11,FRail lines are expected to be busy
OL,12,Fduring the day with affected
OL,13,Fpassengers reminded that tickets
OL,14,Fpurchased for Monday 1 April will be
OL,15,Fvalid for travel on Tuesday 2 April
OL,16,Fand customers are encouraged to travel
OL,17,Ftomorrow if possible.
